definitions.definition: To play a deceitful confidence trick on (someone); to swindle , to trick ; also, to carry out an act of mischief on (someone); to prank .
To play a deceitful confidence trick; also, to carry out an act of mischief.

main_definition: ( transitive ) To play a deceitful confidence trick on (someone); to swindle , to trick ; also, to carry out an act of mischief on (someone); to prank .
secondary_definitions: ( intransitive ) To play a deceitful confidence trick; also, to carry out an act of mischief.
